replies.msg:
@charles_watts: Guendouzi I think will be sold. I'll be very surprised if he's not now. He's only got 2 yrs left on his contract, he isn't responding in the way Arteta wants. If Arsenal are going to sell it will be this summer, he's someone you expect they'll get good money for.<br />
<br />
I would not be surprised if Lacazette gets sold, especially if they can convince Aubameyang to stay. They will see it as an opportunity to get some money in, he only has 2 years left on his contract, so something has got to happen with Lacazette.'

